# MVP Delivery Rules

- Prefer the simplest implementation that ships MVP scope first:
  - Basic chat flow
  - Rule-based symptom classification (before advanced AI)
  - Supabase data query
  - Copay calculation
  - Hospital comparison and recommendation
- Build in phases: simple rules first, AI enhancement second, optimization later.
- When uncertain, choose clarity and maintainability over premature complexity.

## Quality expectations

- Any change touching `reglas_cobertura` must include documentation and reproducible sample data in `database/`.
- Add or update tests when business rules change (copay, ranking, specialty mapping).
- Keep responses and UI output understandable for non-technical end users.
